*
   * Get default beat pattern for a given numerator and denominator.
   * @param {number} num
   * @param {number} denom
   * @return {number[]}
   *
   * @example
   * Time.defaultBeatPattern(4, 4)  => [1, 1, 1, 1]
   * Time.defaultBeatPattern(6, 8)  => [3, 3]
